Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.89,0:00:53.00,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}張りつめた空気が好き
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.56,0:00:58.90,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}高まる鼓動広がってゆくよ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.90,0:01:05.05,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}深く息吸い込んだなら
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.53,0:01:10.29,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}もう前しか見えないわ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.54,0:01:15.36,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}誰も代わる事出来ない
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.48,0:01:18.24,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}私しか歩けない道
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.41,0:01:21.28,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}その涙も全て
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.44,0:01:24.42,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}輝きはじめる
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.62,0:01:29.07,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}だから思いきり振り上げた
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.32,0:01:32.13,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}手のひらに宿る{\fs26}POWER
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.42,0:01:34.52,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}迷わずにまっすぐに
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.66,0:01:37.40,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}明日へと行くよ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.57,0:01:41.17,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}ほんのまばたきの瞬間に
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.41,0:01:44.12,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}叶えるよ夢の{\fs26}STORY
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.38,0:01:46.45,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}儚くて遠くても
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.99,0:01:49.65,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}諦めないわいつも
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.88,0:01:51.58,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}私だけの
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.85,0:01:56.47,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(0,300)\fs26}BAMBOOBEAT{\r}を鳴らして
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.89,0:00:53.00,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}喜歡著緊張的空氣
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.56,0:00:58.90,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}興奮起來走向更廣闊的天地
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.90,0:01:05.05,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}深呼一口氣
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.53,0:01:10.29,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}只專注於眼前的事物
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.54,0:01:15.36,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}誰都無法替代
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.48,0:01:18.24,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}只有我才能前進的道路
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.41,0:01:21.28,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}連同那份淚水
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.44,0:01:24.42,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}全部開始閃耀
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.62,0:01:29.07,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}因此將宿於手中的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.32,0:01:32.13,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}盡情揮揚吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.42,0:01:34.52,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}果斷地  徑直地
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.66,0:01:37.40,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}向著明天全力進發
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.57,0:01:41.17,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}在轉瞬即逝之間
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.41,0:01:44.12,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}實現那夢中的故事
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.38,0:01:46.45,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}無論它多麼虛幻和遙遠
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.99,0:01:49.65,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}我也絕不會放棄
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.88,0:01:51.58,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}和僅屬於我的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.85,0:01:56.47,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(0,300)}竹劍節奏響徹永遠
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.04,0:22:22.72,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fs24\fad(300,0)}I'm Calling the STAR RISE
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.95,0:22:27.74,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}夕闇に  輝き出す  願いたち
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.04,0:22:34.13,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}この手の中 降りてきて 流れ星…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.16,0:22:55.19,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}窓辺で素足のまま  夜を見上げて
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.64,0:23:02.22,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}眠れない 月明かり ひとり
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.09,0:23:10.09,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}目の前を ちらついてく 昼間の私
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.70,0:23:17.43,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}自分だけ 空回りで もどかしいまま
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.71,0:23:20.39,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fs24}I'm Calling the STAR RISE
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.68,0:23:25.43,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}目を閉じて  心の声  聞いてる
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.72,0:23:32.27,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}まだ知らない 私に出会いたい
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.43,0:23:35.27,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fs24}I'm Calling the STAR RISE
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.52,0:23:40.27,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}まばゆく  輝いてる  願いたち
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.60,0:23:47.95,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}この手の中 降りてきて 流れ星…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.04,0:22:22.72,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(300,0)}I'm Calling the STAR RISE
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.95,0:22:27.74,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}暮色中閃耀著的那小小心願
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.04,0:22:34.13,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}寄於手中  希望流星能為我實現…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.16,0:22:55.19,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}在窗邊光著腳丫  仰望著夜空
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.64,0:23:02.22,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}唯有無法入眠的月光相伴
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.09,0:23:10.09,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}眼前浮現出午時的自己
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.70,0:23:17.43,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}只是徒勞得令人著急
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.71,0:23:20.39,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I'm Calling the STAR RISE
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.68,0:23:25.43,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}閉上眼睛傾聽心中的聲音
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.72,0:23:32.27,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}依然無法得知  它想與我相見
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.43,0:23:35.27,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I'm Calling the STAR RISE
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.52,0:23:40.27,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}光輝而耀眼的那小小心願
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.60,0:23:47.95,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}寄於手中  希望流星能為我實現…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.01,0:02:09.01,title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,0)}第16話\N紀梨乃的缺席與預選大會
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.04,0:00:28.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.44,0:00:31.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經是夏天了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.02,0:02:10.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.19,0:02:13.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紀梨乃今天又請假啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.30,0:02:14.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,連著兩天了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.87,0:02:15.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.05,0:02:17.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真少見呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.41,0:02:22.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她可是就算發燒也依然勉強自己就像個笨蛋一樣精神的人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.50,0:02:24.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不是身體相當不舒服啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.39,0:02:30.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紀梨乃前輩虛弱的樣子？我可想像不來
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.22,0:02:32.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你有發簡訊問她嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.96,0:02:36.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發了  昨天5次  今天6次了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.41,0:02:39.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你啊  一到這個時候就很積極了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.14,0:02:45.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是  她根本不回覆
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.88,0:02:49.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紀梨乃…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.68,0:02:58.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都說了  比賽的時候哪有用雙刀…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.31,0:03:01.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.05,0:03:07.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我總有…一種很不好的預感
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.35,0:03:09.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好的預感是指？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.18,0:03:12.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了嘛  不過2天沒來你也太誇張了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.24,0:03:15.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂！你要去哪裡？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.00,0:03:18.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要直接去紀梨乃家一趟
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.12,0:03:27.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她去了…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.48,0:03:29.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還穿著劍道服
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.31,0:03:32.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼又一個人隨意跑掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.32,0:03:35.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是第六感
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.03,0:03:41.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為鞘前輩和紀梨乃前輩交往最久
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.49,0:03:43.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以才能感覺得到
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.19,0:03:46.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那與平日不同的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.61,0:03:47.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不尋常的氣氛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.06,0:03:57.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紀梨乃——！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.81,0:04:01.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紀梨乃這個笨蛋！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.65,0:04:04.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是個就算發高燒  站都站不穩
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.82,0:04:08.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也會勉強來學校  在大家面前裝作很有精神
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.84,0:04:11.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一回家就倒下的笨蛋！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.10,0:04:21.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣的紀梨乃
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.51,0:04:22.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然連續兩天毫無音訊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.50,0:04:25.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太奇怪了！一定出事了！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.44,0:04:27.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紀梨乃！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.02,0:04:28.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紀梨乃！！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.20,0:04:32.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紀梨乃——！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.22,0:04:37.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來囉  讓您久等
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.96,0:04:42.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杏味可樂餅4個和果醬夾肉三明治一共750元
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.82,0:04:44.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你  紀梨乃
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.90,0:04:46.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多謝惠顧～
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.30,0:04:49.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀  怎麼了  小鞘
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.99,0:04:52.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,穿成那樣怎麼了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.34,0:04:53.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什麼事？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.18,0:04:55.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.38,0:05:03.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,炸肉餅…6個…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.49,0:05:04.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多謝惠顧～
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.46,0:05:08.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起！因為補習所以遲到了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.29,0:05:12.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒  大家在吃點心嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.21,0:05:15.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好吃哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.48,0:05:17.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來  聰莉你也快來吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.70,0:05:21.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過  為什麼有炸肉餅
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.86,0:05:23.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我剛買回來
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.16,0:05:26.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼在社團活動中跑去買炸肉餅呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.45,0:05:30.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吵死了！管那麼多？吃就是了！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.96,0:05:34.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什麼關係嘛  紀梨乃也很有精神
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.62,0:05:36.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這又是常見的小鞘妄想啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.19,0:05:39.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為這次真的和平時不一樣嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.03,0:05:42.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼  我的炸肉餅呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.61,0:05:44.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經沒有了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.88,0:05:53.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是  為什麼紀梨乃前輩必須要請假在家看店呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.24,0:05:56.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是因為…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.61,0:05:58.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.25,0:06:04.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.27,0:06:06.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  紀梨乃
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.73,0:06:07.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在做什麼啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.27,0:06:09.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看就明白了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.80,0:06:11.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第二套廣播體操啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.77,0:06:14.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行啦  快躺回床上去
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.61,0:06:17.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快快快  進被窩進被窩
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.17,0:06:20.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天店裡怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.88,0:06:23.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要緊  今天是我看店的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.87,0:06:25.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你今天又請假了？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.44,0:06:29.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為  爸爸一個人忙不過來嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.19,0:06:32.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過明天阿姨會過來
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.38,0:06:35.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎？太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.80,0:06:40.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是還要準備劍道大賽嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.10,0:06:44.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  所以這個週末我是來不了了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.36,0:06:46.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唉  好可惜
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.10,0:06:49.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難得我想幫你去加油的說
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.69,0:06:51.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行了行了你就好好躺著吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.88,0:06:52.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.60,0:07:11.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎  所以你代替你母親去看店啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.69,0:07:14.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,造成大家的困擾真的很對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.34,0:07:21.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說你  就不能給我們說清楚嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.04,0:07:23.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.48,0:07:24.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為太忙所以沒注意…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.98,0:07:27.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是啊！還無視我的簡訊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.05,0:07:28.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.31,0:07:32.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然還讓我淪為去買炸肉餅的跑腿
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.72,0:07:33.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為啥？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.66,0:07:37.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼  你母親的病況怎麼樣了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.95,0:07:39.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為過度疲勞
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.02,0:07:42.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然我看現在已經精神十足了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.46,0:07:46.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過因為還要做各種檢查  所以還要住院三天
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.78,0:07:48.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,過度疲勞啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.84,0:07:50.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在店裡很忙碌吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.03,0:07:53.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的  不僅很忙碌
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.62,0:08:02.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還通宵跑去參加什麼喬尼斯的演唱會
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.37,0:08:05.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是拿她沒辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.61,0:08:07.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好年輕啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.24,0:08:11.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過  身體已經不是年輕時候的樣子了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.73,0:08:13.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也這樣說結果她生氣了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.00,0:08:17.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  紀梨乃前輩回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.36,0:08:19.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.78,0:08:21.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好精神哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.07,0:08:25.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼嘛  別讓人擔心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.17,0:08:27.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起啦  橡子頭
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.46,0:08:30.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  要補上休息漏下的分量囉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.43,0:08:31.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.47,0:08:36.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天就是縣北預賽了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.08,0:08:38.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖說不是真正的預賽  但不要鬆懈
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.46,0:08:40.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果輸了就沒戲了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.02,0:08:41.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.94,0:08:46.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,胴！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.30,0:08:47.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.17,0:08:49.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呀～輸啦輸啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.31,0:08:52.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你成長了呢  小都都
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.40,0:08:53.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝誇獎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.01,0:08:55.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紀梨乃～
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.84,0:08:58.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你來當小珠的對手啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.40,0:09:01.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已經被榨乾了…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.63,0:09:02.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.75,0:09:03.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好喲
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.35,0:09:06.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼  小都都  等會再來哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.08,0:09:07.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.75,0:09:21.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鞘
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.51,0:09:22.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咋了？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.88,0:09:24.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天你可要好好振作哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.25,0:09:26.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太失禮了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.47,0:09:28.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一向都很振作
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.25,0:09:33.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然在死撐  但紀梨乃一直在擔心她母親
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.54,0:09:38.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是為了明天的預賽  不希望大家替她操心
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.89,0:09:43.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你作為她的朋友  好好支持她吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.15,0:09:48.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.68,0:09:51.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種事情不用你說我也明白
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.47,0:09:54.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紀梨乃的事情我比老師你更清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.56,0:09:56.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紀梨乃就交給我吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.05,0:09:59.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天我就是部長了！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.81,0:10:01.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久等了～小鞘
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.73,0:10:02.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦！紀梨乃！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.29,0:10:04.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.32,0:10:06.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回家囉！哦！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.18,0:10:08.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…知道啦…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.15,0:10:09.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再來是…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.52,0:10:16.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託了  大將
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.63,0:10:17.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.70,0:10:20.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請你拯救部長  也就是紀梨乃！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.81,0:10:22.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…怎麼做…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.08,0:10:24.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那還用說
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.53,0:10:27.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之大將就是要過關斬將一路贏下去
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.35,0:10:36.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.58,0:10:41.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,噢！噢噢噢！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.11,0:10:44.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了鼓勵紀梨乃  我現在要獻唱了！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.36,0:10:53.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡就是預選賽的會場嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.45,0:10:55.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我來了！全國大賽！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.99,0:10:57.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瞧好了！三島！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.57,0:11:00.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這次我一定要打倒你！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.35,0:11:03.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是這個氣勢  清村君！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.82,0:11:07.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放心！你與我的組合是天下無敵的！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.04,0:11:10.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杉小路！那不是棒球嗎？！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.41,0:11:12.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然而這裡不是…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.50,0:11:13.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打劍道的地方嗎？！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.06,0:11:16.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回去吧  清村
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.23,0:11:17.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回哪裡？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.17,0:11:20.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找個地方
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.23,0:11:20.08,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（這兩個笨蛋是出自原作、即土塚理弘的漫畫作品「清村和杉小路」）
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.83,0:11:27.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,胴——！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.84,0:11:29.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好！腹部有效！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.49,0:11:30.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不愧是小莉莉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.92,0:11:32.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拿下先鋒！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.52,0:11:34.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.35,0:11:41.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兩勝一負！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.65,0:11:43.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只差一勝！只差一勝！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.77,0:11:47.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紀梨乃部長  加油！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.27,0:11:48.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託了紀梨乃！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.35,0:11:58.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開始！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.60,0:12:00.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.83,0:12:05.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,胴！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.91,0:12:08.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好強
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.01,0:12:10.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一下子就連贏兩場
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.11,0:12:12.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太帥了！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.30,0:12:16.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做得好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.18,0:12:18.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紀梨乃部長  贏得漂亮！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.54,0:12:24.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還以為這傢伙會因為母親住院而無法集中精神
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.82,0:12:25.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結果卻正相反
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.74,0:12:28.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比平日更加專注於比賽
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.01,0:12:31.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為精神緊繃
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.92,0:12:35.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以才提高了集中力  發揮出超乎水平的實力
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.30,0:12:39.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來用不著我出場了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.25,0:12:42.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  不愧是紀梨乃
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.43,0:12:44.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再來是…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.83,0:12:47.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.97,0:12:49.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦！贏了贏了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.40,0:12:50.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不愧是小珠
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.27,0:12:56.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,進入二回戰了！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.60,0:12:57.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.90,0:13:00.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天狀態大好啊  紀梨乃
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.69,0:13:03.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,連勝兩場  太厲害了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.50,0:13:05.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.28,0:13:09.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小西同學
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.08,0:13:11.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老師在找你哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.16,0:13:13.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思  我就去
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.10,0:13:21.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個人…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.27,0:13:23.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了  你認識嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.31,0:13:30.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  她是在上次地區大賽上獲得團體冠軍的東城高的大將
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.43,0:13:34.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果他們再贏一場  就和我們碰上了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.95,0:13:37.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是說  她是小珠的對手了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.44,0:13:39.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒問題
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.55,0:13:41.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地區預賽沒人打得贏小珠
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.79,0:13:42.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是說啦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.80,0:13:45.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.06,0:13:48.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,關於她有些奇怪的傳言
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.15,0:13:51.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對手在對戰前受傷啦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.07,0:13:53.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鞋子裡被放圖釘啦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.27,0:13:55.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,防具被藏起來啦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.80,0:13:59.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是她做的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.61,0:14:01.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是傳言啦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.72,0:14:05.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別傻了  怎麼可能真有這種事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.36,0:14:09.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定又是輸給她的傢伙們四處散佈的怨言啦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.74,0:14:11.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女人真可怕啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.00,0:14:14.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我問問小鞘你是聽誰說的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.88,0:14:17.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我朋友的朋友說的…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.64,0:14:19.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看  來了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.40,0:14:20.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朋友的朋友說的…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.23,0:14:22.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都市傳說嗎你
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.66,0:14:23.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吵死啦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.67,0:14:26.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也不是說真的相信了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.80,0:14:27.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過是學生的大賽
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.21,0:14:30.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會有人做到這種地步嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.59,0:14:32.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太不現實啦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.64,0:14:34.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我都說了是傳聞！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.13,0:14:37.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了  宮崎同學？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.88,0:14:39.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聰莉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.29,0:14:41.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給我買茶去
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.89,0:14:42.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.20,0:14:44.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我渴了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.55,0:14:47.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能不能給我買瓶茶來？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.73,0:14:49.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.64,0:14:55.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有我…一局都沒有拿下…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.28,0:14:59.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  小都都
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.01,0:15:01.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了  段郎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.75,0:15:05.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃便當囉  大家都在外面等著
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.32,0:15:08.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  嗯  對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.01,0:15:14.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小都都
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.48,0:15:19.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然輸了  但你已經盡了最大努力了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.03,0:15:22.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的好帥哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.95,0:15:36.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  我很帥對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.67,0:15:46.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各位！只差一勝了！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.11,0:15:49.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,東城高也和我們一樣是兩戰零敗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.37,0:15:53.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是不打贏他們  就沒法進軍縣預賽哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.55,0:15:57.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在我們的氣勢可以衝破天際  擋也擋不住哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.51,0:15:58.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對！沒錯！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.21,0:16:00.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們5個人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.85,0:16:04.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,5個人對吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.07,0:16:06.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？小莉莉呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.06,0:16:07.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.54,0:16:09.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,買了這麼久
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.95,0:16:12.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宮崎同學要不高興了！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.23,0:16:16.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀  真對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.74,0:16:18.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.85,0:16:20.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我太不小心了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.94,0:16:21.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.29,0:16:22.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.02,0:16:37.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦  你在做什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.27,0:16:40.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快點吃便當啦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.51,0:16:42.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起  碰到不少事情
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.14,0:16:44.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我馬上就來
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.17,0:16:47.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個  你托我買的茶…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.97,0:16:49.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝  辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.42,0:16:53.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為弄掉後  被狠狠踩了一腳
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.06,0:16:57.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又沒有錢重新買…就成了這樣了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.88,0:17:01.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.87,0:17:02.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你  聰莉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.63,0:17:06.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給你錢  零錢就不用找了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.87,0:17:09.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.16,0:17:13.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說東啊  你的便當是什麼樣的？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.49,0:17:14.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小心哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.65,0:17:16.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這大叔可是專門盯著菜的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.11,0:17:19.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係的  老師
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.93,0:17:23.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我拜託媽媽也替大家準備了很多份
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.24,0:17:30.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,土星機？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.99,0:17:33.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搞錯了…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.42,0:17:34.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不哭不哭
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.93,0:17:47.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂喂  怎麼了啊紀梨乃
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.21,0:17:49.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎麼一口也不吃啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.36,0:17:52.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣你怎麼去打下午的比賽嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.41,0:17:54.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多吃點多吃點
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.34,0:17:55.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好歡樂
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.19,0:17:58.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也要！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.15,0:18:01.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行！段君！部長要升天了！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.91,0:18:07.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和大家一起吃便當  真開心
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.84,0:18:16.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小西前輩
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.72,0:18:18.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.22,0:18:23.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  找到了找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.79,0:18:26.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前輩  差不多該去開會了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.59,0:18:28.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝  我馬上去
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.94,0:18:38.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下一戰的室江高相當有實力
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.77,0:18:42.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,特別是大將川添相當厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.05,0:18:45.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  那個小不點啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.29,0:18:46.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新入部員吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.08,0:18:49.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,室江找了個好部員呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.26,0:18:53.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,室江高和我們之間只有獲勝的才能出線
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.38,0:18:56.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,男生已經戰敗了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.26,0:18:58.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以你們女生要好好加油
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.04,0:19:01.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊～我們學校的男生太沒用了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.81,0:19:04.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難得來加油還輸這麼慘
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.56,0:19:06.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又沒人長得帥
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.86,0:19:08.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這方面還是女生強呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.53,0:19:15.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們不會輸在這樣的預選賽上
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.72,0:19:16.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會贏的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.55,0:19:18.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.82,0:19:22.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那種小不點怎麼打得過小西前輩
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.47,0:19:26.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先前的個人賽要是小西前輩出賽的話絕對是優勝呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.38,0:19:29.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝  我會加油的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.35,0:19:46.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼扔下我一個啊  那幫傢伙！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.26,0:19:47.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫我一聲啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.26,0:20:16.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.60,0:20:29.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,室江高中  川添珠姬選手
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.78,0:20:31.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,川添珠姬選手
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.77,0:20:33.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您的家人到場
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.70,0:20:35.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請到停車場會面
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.13,0:20:37.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.87,0:20:39.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你爸爸？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.13,0:20:41.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有聯絡過你嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.90,0:20:43.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼也沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.72,0:20:46.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之去看看吧  還有時間
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.32,0:20:49.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起  我去了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.73,0:20:52.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種時候有什麼事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.79,0:20:57.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別是壞事就好…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.14,0:21:38.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請問是川添珠姬同學嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.45,0:21:41.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.69,0:21:43.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能耽誤你一下嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.62,0:21:44.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.54,0:21:49.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個  等等  要帶我去哪裡？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.31,0:21:50.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來啦來啦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.50,0:21:52.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你太可愛了  珠姬同學
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.41,0:21:55.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我馬上還有比賽  不趕快回去的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.69,0:21:57.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只一下只一下
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.61,0:22:05.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大成功
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.99,0:22:07.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜囉
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.39,0:22:09.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比賽結束前你就待在這裡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.29,0:22:10.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.68,0:22:16.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把門打開！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.80,0:22:18.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打開！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.43,0:23:53.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,清村！竹劍被動畫化了啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.95,0:23:56.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你夠慢啊！剛剛我們不是出場了嗎？就剛剛！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.98,0:23:58.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  不過下話好像就是最終話了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.07,0:24:01.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你少騙人了！還要繼續十來話吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.33,0:24:01.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下集是
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.07,0:24:03.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「第17話  光與陰」
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.72,0:24:05.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定是那從宇宙來的光物大師
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.66,0:24:07.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,與暗地裡操縱著政府的大驚小怪船長之間
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.67,0:24:09.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,展開的激動人心的大戰
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.40,0:24:11.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什麼動畫啊  超讓人想看
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.24,0:24:12.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好期待下一話啊
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.13,0:24:15.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  那下次咱們也出來吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.41,0:24:16.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉  我還有事
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.71,0:24:18.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我得趕去和光物大師展開激動人心的大戰
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.58,0:24:19.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來是你嗎？！
